    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You've practiced casting powers in the midst of combat, learning techniques that grant you the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You have advantage on Constitution saving throws that you make to maintain your concentration on a power when you take damage.</li>\n<li>Once per round, when a hostile creature provokes an opportunity attack from you, you can use your reaction to cast a power at the creature, rather than making an opportunity attack. The power must have a casting time of 1 action and must target only that creature.</li></ul>",
